    "## Phase 5 — Refusal across (intact/ablated) x (harmful/harmless) x N"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "4f6cb00f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
